    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "A Comprehensive Power BI Grower Portal Dashboard"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 designed and implemented a Power BI-based Grower Portal Dashboard. This provided an interactive and real-time visibility into growers’ operations and their contracts. The key features of the solution include:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Strategic Optimization of Existing Reports"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "We deeply analyzed Savills’ existing reporting infrastructure to highlight bottlenecks and refine reporting logic for maximized performance and data accuracy."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Interactive Widgets for Deep Insights"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Tracking of subcontracts by status, field operations, and crop acreage. Real-time yield estimates compare against historical data, and county-level acreage changes highlight trends over time."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Dynamic Filtering Capabilities"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Global filters for Crop Year, Division (VFO, YHS), and individual growers enable users to tailor their data views instantly."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Intuitive Drill-Down Functionality"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Any segment within a chart is clickable, which highlights detailed lists of contracts, growers, fields, varieties, and acres in a tabular format, along with downloadable option."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Role-Based Access"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The designed permission matrix enhances security. The categorized users are granted access based on their roles and assigned growers."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "TRANSFORM YOUR GROWER DATA",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
